PrecisAppointment of BRUCE S. ELWOOD of Dundas, Ontario; CÉLINE CHAMBERLAND of Iqaluit, Nunavut; CHRIS TROWBRIDGE of Westport, Ontario; and REBEKAH UQI WILLIAMS of Iqaluit, Nunavut, to be part-time members of the National Parole Board, Ontario Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years.
